I am a wizard, my spells should be more mana efficient and cast faster, but they should also do MUCH more damage per cast than any other class. No I dont think I should have a 2k damage unresistable spell for 200mana, but I do think that no DD or bolt from any class should do within 200dmg of a nuke from a wizard of the level, nor do I think the draught line of spells should exist as they are, our damage should have continued on an upward scale from IC, or have &quot;Kunark/Velious&quot; only spells instead of scaling our damage to old world standards.<br>
<br>
Example-<br>
Draught of Fire lvl51-643dmg, 215mana-2.99dmg per mana<br>
It should be-Draught of Fire 1220dmg,420mana-2.90dmg per mana, castable in Kunark/Velious Only<br>
<br>
Yes, my version is not as mana efficient, yes you could cast two draughts to achieve the same effect, thats not the point, and if you don't get the point then you are to far gone, may god have mercy on your soul, because verant certainly will not.<br>
<br>
Darret 58 Wizard<br>
Dragonriders of Norrath, Fennin Ro <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.showMessage?topicID=342.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.showMessage?topicID=358.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.emailToFriend?topicID=348.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.threadControl?topicID=348.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=348.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=348.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm1">General Discussion<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm3">Trade Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm4">Rant Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm8">Mob Dropped Spells<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm10">Class Balance & Class Bugs<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm22">Out of Mana<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm27">PVP Forum